testcase.name:
respondTo - validates method existence - Expected 'class TestClass {
    testMethod() { return 'test' }
    anotherMethod() { return 'another' }
  }' to respondTo 'testMethod'

respondTo - validates method existence - Expected 'class TestClass {
    testMethod() { return 'test' }
    anotherMethod() { return 'another' }
  }' to respondTo 'anotherMethod'

respondTo - with itself for static methods - Expected 'class MyClass {
    static staticMethod() { return 'static' }
    instanceMethod() { return 'instance' }
  }' to respondTo 'staticMethod'

respondTo - with itself for static methods - Expected 'class MyClass {
    static staticMethod() { return 'static' }
    instanceMethod() { return 'instance' }
  }' to not itself respondTo 'instanceMethod'

respondTo - with itself for static methods - Expected 'class MyClass {
    static staticMethod() { return 'static' }
    instanceMethod() { return 'instance' }
  }' to respondTo 'instanceMethod'
